title: Eddie Izzard - All 7 shows
description:
Here it is, a reseed on Eddie Izzard&#039;s 7 shows he has recorded (so far):



- Live at the Ambassador&#039;s         1h 24min
- Unrepeatable                     1h 11min
- Glorious                         1h 40min
- Definite Article                 1h 50min
- Dress To Kill                    1h 54min
- Circle                           1h 21min
- Sexie                            1h 36min

All are in good quality, even if "Live at the Ambassador&#039;s" has an irritating sound in the background sometimes, but it&#039;s neglectable. Also, in the end of "Circle", there&#039;s some buckfutting with the sound/video, but fully watchable with some patience.
